    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像素旅人-Pixel Traveler是一款 rogue-lite 动作游戏，可以自由编辑技能连携触发链条。 设计自己的技能组合，每次创造不同的协同效应；利用有限的资源，互相转换合成获得理想的技能组合，调试发挥最大的效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技能链条的简单例子</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        普攻触发技能=&gt;技能持续时间=&gt;触发下一个技能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/504bb2ae6a01b9ce84808d853772fab9.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/504bb2ae6a01b9ce84808d853772fab9.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.poster.avif?t=1749351139\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.webm?t=1749351139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.mp4?t=1749351139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          游戏有丰富的积累充能方式，以方便玩家编辑多样的技能链条</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还有丰富的装备：鼠标范围索敌，自动索敌，移动攻击，自动攻击等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以自由的设置：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        立体视角（透视视角）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/269ce7f43422dbcd803a72615a53057c.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/269ce7f43422dbcd803a72615a53057c.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=450 /></span>        扁平视角（平行视角）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/1998231053655de0cb2de1012af004c3.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/1998231053655de0cb2de1012af004c3.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
